        <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>By accessing <strong>crestmoreresearch.com</strong> or using any Crestmore service, you represent that you are at least 18 years of age and have the legal capacity to enter into these Terms. If you are accessing our services on behalf of an organisation, you represent that you have authority to bind that organisation.</p>

